The Torch is burning in Dubai for the second time.
One of the world's largest residential skyscrapers was on fire in Dubai on Friday, with firefighters having to evacuate all residents of the 337-meter-high and 79-story buildings.
This is the second fire in the high-rise building in the last two years, which bears the aptly named The Torch.
